    <item>
      <title>Anti-Jew, anti-Zionist, anti-American hate blinds many to the Iranian regime’s evils - opinion</title>
      <link>https://www.jpost.com/jerusalem-report/article-888709</link>
      <description> &lt;img align='right' src='https://images.jpost.com/image/upload/f_auto,fl_lossy/q_auto/c_fill,g_faces:center,h_3755,w_5633/709570' alt='People march during a protest against the war in Iran on March 2, 2026 in New York, New York. U.S. (photo credit:  Adam Gray/Getty Images)' title='People march during a protest against the war in Iran on March 2, 2026 in New York, New York. U.S. (photo credit:  Adam Gray/Getty Images)' /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;From Times Square to major newsrooms, moral confusion over Israel and Trump is muting outrage at Tehran’s repression, terror, and slaughter of its own civilians.&lt;br /&gt; </description>
      <Photographer> Adam Gray/Getty Images</Photographer>
